[{"Code":"en","Content":"<p data-block-id=\"mlacdddx-kgwovx-483\"><a id=\"_s6tqfgcj75rk\" display=\"false\"></a>KYC CN Activation Flow</p><h2 data-block-id=\"mlacdddy-ae9i6l-484\"><a id=\"_ludjd4rjhnda\" display=\"false\"></a>Admin Dashboard Workflow</h2><p data-block-id=\"mlacdddy-muq0w5-485\">The Admin Dashboard is an interface used by MO Agents to perform the Know Your Customer (KYC) process for merchants onboarding with Xendit. KYC is an essential verification step that helps us confirm the identity, legitimacy, and risk profile of each merchant to meet regulatory requirements and protect our platform.</p><p data-block-id=\"mlacdddy-rw2uxd-486\">This section describes the complete Admin Dashboard workflow from initial registration from the merchant side to how MO processes the merchant’s application.</p><p data-block-id=\"mlacdddy-uxk02c-487\">The Admin Dashboard workflow includes the following steps:</p><h1 data-block-id=\"mlacdddy-r10g94-488\"><a id=\"_b857wonu6rq3\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:51px;\"><col style=\"width:316px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:86px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"51\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdddz-okx722-489\"><strong>No.</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"316\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdddz-g17pjw-490\"><strong>Step</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdddz-vubvve-491\"><strong>Screen Shot</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"86\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde0-u7zx0f-492\"><strong>Who</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"51\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde0-axs63i-493\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"316\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde1-qfhd8f-494\">Login to Admin Dashboard <a href=\"https://admin-dashboard.tidnex.com/customer-management-v2/5fbb793afbde30171eae99f4\"><u>Here</u></a></p><ul data-block-id=\"mlacdde1-9c5h3q-495\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacdde1-rnr360-496\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2su-l07b12-250\">go Onboarding Management</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacdde1-truyfn-497\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2su-up6taa-251\">change country view to Singapore</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde1-d2yl2o-498\"><em>*Ask your manager for regional access</em></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde1-k66r39-499\"><em><img data-block-id=\"mlacdde2-7756ko-500\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-6d3wqno4.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></em></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"86\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde2-ofu43g-501\"><em>MO</em></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"51\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde3-6c5ln4-502\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"316\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde3-v9lmso-503\">Check Risk Score</p><ul data-block-id=\"mlacdde3-bz5cr3-504\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacdde3-83nk24-505\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sv-vi3w3e-252\">Pass for those not showing as “very high risk”</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacdde3-cc34zb-506\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sv-dhh8pu-253\">Escalate to Risk Team for “very high risk”, #risk-request# first as for cases on fraud activities</p></li></ul></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde4-kglf3n-507\"><em><img data-block-id=\"mlacdde4-q2nk5n-508\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-9k05i2r1.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></em></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"86\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde4-pacy0p-509\"><em>MO</em></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"51\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde4-vybp8t-510\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"316\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde5-uiem2s-511\">Click on start KYC &gt; click Screen Merchant</p><ul data-block-id=\"mlacdde5-717v56-512\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacdde5-0lqi5q-513\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sw-tkwb9y-254\">Tick “Digital” or “Non-digital” for Industry Type</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacdde5-f7vt4l-514\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sw-drkpdp-255\">Tick or cross for:</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacdde5-f1svyy-515\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sw-muv70q-256\">Business Registration Name, Products, Pricing &amp; Identity (name &amp; contact, etc)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacdde5-rns1ie-516\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sw-kiut9r-257\">Check for incomplete/wrong/unclear documents</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacdde5-7z4gtc-517\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sw-1wpb2o-258\">Click on “Save and Screen” </p></li></ul></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde5-tws3sj-518\"><em><img data-block-id=\"mlacdde5-5cor7q-519\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-8s6gchbm.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></em></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"86\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde6-3oilhg-520\"><em>MO</em></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"51\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde6-uxsjmy-521\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"316\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde6-pacayq-522\">Screening Status and Actions</p><ul data-block-id=\"mlacdde6-zdech8-523\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacdde6-uusu7d-524\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sw-xhoev2-259\">No Alert–No action needed</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacdde6-ozhwj8-525\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sw-tfhlq3-260\">Negative–No action needed</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacdde6-etvwbw-526\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sw-qzeq1b-261\">Decision required–Check on ComplyAdvantage</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacdde6-hc804i-527\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sw-zlql9o-262\">Screening failed–Rescreen</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacdde6-kgtoqn-528\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sw-ud6guj-263\">Others–triggered by MO action on Comply Advantage</p></li></ul></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde7-dajn1l-529\"><em><img data-block-id=\"mlacdde7-hv6pp9-530\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-0hrnpjrg.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></em></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"86\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde7-v3bwjy-531\">MO,Compliance</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"51\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde8-7mj406-532\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"316\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde8-6y6anp-533\">Decision on whether we should pass and click on “Action”</p><ul data-block-id=\"mlacdde8-mt9hzs-534\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacdde8-yefxjq-535\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sx-w2r8av-264\">Pass–if pass for all KYC &amp; ComplyAdvantage</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacdde8-az99kt-536\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sx-rc80nk-265\">Skip Screening &amp; Pass–All merchants need to be screened</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacdde8-6s6ynh-537\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sx-g041zl-266\">Request Resubmission–request for additional documents support</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacdde8-6wrdok-538\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sx-teqf9b-267\">Fail–if not pass KYC/ComplyAdvantage</p></li></ul></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde8-bu2mvb-539\"><em><img data-block-id=\"mlacdde8-8qn46x-540\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-tql3wsmt.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></em></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"86\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde9-2gjoxe-541\">MO</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mlacdde9-5jlld7-542\"><a id=\"_hhka5axmas5\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mlacdde9-ocky8u-543\"><a id=\"_53xiufrsahz7\" display=\"false\"></a>Xendit Stakeholders</h2><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde9-k4zoy0-544\">The Merchant Onboarding (MO) process involves close collaboration across multiple teams within Xendit. Each stakeholder plays a distinct role in ensuring that merchants are reviewed thoroughly from business, legal, risk, and operational perspectives. Below are the stakeholders for chinese regions:</p><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdde9-93n3st-545\"><strong>Department</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddea-l9bj5q-546\"><strong>PIC</strong></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddea-liv23l-547\"><strong>PIC Role</strong></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddea-9gvmby-548\">Compliance</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeb-94prtb-549\"><a><u>Hong Jie Lim</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeb-6jx0vr-550\">Deviation and onboarding compliance concerns</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeb-7vgo0k-551\">Merchant Operations</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddec-q36pym-552\">For Account Activation:<a><u>Rachel DiercieJinghang Gui</u></a><br type=\"inline\"><br type=\"inline\">For Channel Activation:<br type=\"inline\">TH: <a><u>Kavissara (Praew) Apiratrueangwut</u></a><br type=\"inline\">VN: <a><u>Thai Phan</u></a><br type=\"inline\">PH: <a><u>Raffy John Panes</u></a><br type=\"inline\">ID: <a><u>Imaculata Visar</u></a><br type=\"inline\">MY: <a><u>Kon Nee Looi</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddee-h897dk-560\">Account and Channel Activation</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddee-cuuc19-561\">OIM (Onboarding and Implementation)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddee-xgyghd-562\"><a><u>Dinan</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddef-pk0mez-563\">Assist with onboarding regional merchants</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sz-5debst-268\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddef-w5hdh2-564\">Justina</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeg-yzltc1-565\">Provide sign-off prior to go live</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mlacddeg-ejdg4j-566\"><a id=\"_8buvg77yh7b0\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mlacddeg-jurklw-567\"><a id=\"_le7wrrzdv5cd\" display=\"false\"></a>Business Due Diligence</h2><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeg-8ndois-568\">The Business Due Diligence (BDD) process guides MO Agents in verifying a merchant’s business information during onboarding. Agents review the merchant’s website, business description, and industry classification to ensure they align with Xendit’s policies and risk requirements.</p><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeg-qhljif-569\">Below are the general criteria a merchant's website must meet during the verification process:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mlacddeg-i5yepf-570\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacddeg-xkr91f-571\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sz-u7gn78-269\">The website or App must be ready, live, and accessible.</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddeg-lv94qp-572\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sz-93xt3f-270\">The website should match the nature of the business registered with Xendit</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddeg-1vf7ui-573\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sz-b8922q-271\">The website must reflect and match the contact information (such as business email, phone number, business address) registered with Xendit</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddeg-rxd2fh-574\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2sz-ymledk-272\">We prefer websites and apps with catalogs or products with pricing details that are available to purchase via checkout flow.</p></li></ul><h3 data-block-id=\"mlacddeg-pkqc5o-575\"><a id=\"_odercn85vwma\" display=\"false\"></a></h3><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:50px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeg-m2hkig-576\">No</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeh-ni0ey7-577\">Type of Business Proof</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeh-yc4xnq-578\">What to check</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeh-qlzmb0-579\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeh-uargit-580\">Website</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mlacddei-2t2wui-581\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacddei-0e18o3-582\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t0-1uyl7w-273\">Accessible</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddei-qg2heg-583\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t0-nk1co8-274\">Original (no signs of plagiarism)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddei-cqsd79-584\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t0-s65mwc-275\">No signs of suspicious activities (e.g. gambling)</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddei-41ruvk-585\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t0-r2h2jx-276\">Does not contain negative reviews indicating fraud</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddei-a87l1a-586\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t0-xrvbny-277\">Products are clearly present and aligned with the business</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddei-1db35c-587\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t0-swm2hp-278\">Pricing is clearly present and realistic</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddei-wog6zd-588\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t0-fbfbp4-279\">If an App, it must be available on official app stores (Tencent App Store (also known as MyApp), Huawei App Market, and Xiaomi App Store)</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddei-ho93r1-589\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddei-t6uh9i-590\">Photos of Offline Presence </p><p data-block-id=\"mlacddei-4i9tc9-591\">*For non-online merchant only</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddej-0huc2c-592\">One or more of these must be present:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mlacddej-nk24c2-593\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacddej-p5hhlb-594\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t1-k7qcze-280\">Signage with the business name</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mlacddej-fzaz7v-595\"><strong><em><img data-block-id=\"mlacddej-5a1pz8-596\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-s34xgtun.jpg\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></em></strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mlacddej-01ohbk-597\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacddej-hgo27n-598\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t1-acwfm3-281\">(Preferred) Signage with the legal name</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mlacddej-0v2sbl-599\"><strong><em><img data-block-id=\"mlacddej-epbujs-600\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-zakzqkyz.jpg\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></em></strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mlacddej-t2r7sq-601\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacddej-62hvw5-602\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t1-6cpe37-282\">(Preferred) Products that are aligned with the business activity</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mlacddej-f3u3nh-603\"><strong><em><img data-block-id=\"mlacddej-mu9536-604\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-jg1s6t5n.jpg\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"><img data-block-id=\"mlacddej-vwt7a8-605\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-v6tyiaun.jpg\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></em></strong></p><ul data-block-id=\"mlacddej-t5pupq-606\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacddej-8he0er-607\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t1-wxuiwd-283\">(Preferred) Photos match the business pictures that are found online</p></li></ul></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddek-pgsdy7-608\">3</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddek-kcm9pj-609\">Contract between buyer &amp; merchant</p><p data-block-id=\"mlacddek-9us99z-610\">Or transaction record of the online store</p><p data-block-id=\"mlacddek-fb54rl-611\">(Optional)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mlacddek-4v5kfn-612\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacddek-sdfnd6-613\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t1-861p0i-284\">Showing the legal name of the business</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddek-iw4dfr-614\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t1-sgarv8-285\">Showing the trade name of the business</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddek-zbjt7a-615\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t1-1rro0c-286\">Detailing transactions of products that are aligned with the nature of the business</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddek-znetp7-616\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t1-tbiq3n-287\">Convincing visuals (does not look fabricated or poorly/unprofessionally made)</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mlacddek-bwvj5w-617\"><img data-block-id=\"mlacddek-0xg512-618\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-2grzm7ub.jpg\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"><img data-block-id=\"mlacddek-ra1vt4-619\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-fne7izop.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddel-p2yul2-620\">4</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddel-2yildm-621\">Proof of payment (Optional, refer to corporate type)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mlacddel-nfh2qc-622\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacddel-q1g1wd-623\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t2-57cvv0-288\">Showing the legal name of the business as the recipient bank account</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddel-e0uq1z-624\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t2-nan7c0-289\">Showing the amount of transactions that are aligned with their product pricing</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mlacddel-xxmi49-625\"><img data-block-id=\"mlacddel-a1yzvd-626\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-w1jeaa9b.jpg\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddem-zkij0t-627\">5</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddem-zpngj1-628\">Screenshot of communication between merchant and buyer confirming product ordering (Optional)</p><p data-block-id=\"mlacddem-jjz3xf-629\">WeChat is acceptable.</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><ul data-block-id=\"mlacddem-v4orvj-630\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacddem-zcu9hd-631\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t2-xoxrh0-290\">Detailing transactions of products that are aligned with the nature of the business</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddem-74zu2n-632\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t2-235xxa-291\">Convincing visuals (does not look fabricated or poorly/unprofessionally made)</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mlacddem-1l3f7j-633\"><img data-block-id=\"mlacddem-bvngso-634\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-yikas7u2.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mlacddem-7co2yh-635\"><a id=\"_14961d2qvgm\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h2 data-block-id=\"mlacddem-bph5q3-636\"><a id=\"_emoc9dep0n3r\" display=\"false\"></a>Legal Due Diligence</h2><p data-block-id=\"mlacddem-7yo7pn-637\">The Legal Due Diligence (LDD) process enables MO Agents to verify the validity of legal documents submitted by merchants during onboarding. Agents review required documents in the Admin Dashboard and mark them as valid or request resubmission if invalid.</p><p data-block-id=\"mlacddem-0ysl57-638\">The steps below outline the standard workflow for completing LDD checks:</p><h3 data-block-id=\"mlacddem-o7krit-639\"><a id=\"_j1g0ogda31v3\" display=\"false\"></a></h3><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:50px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdden-3tga21-640\">No</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdden-xrn6zw-641\">Document Sample</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdden-kksxcj-642\">What to check</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t3-y4zov7-292\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeo-drtaci-643\">🇭🇰Certificate of Incorporation</p><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeo-h1dxih-644\">HK database: <a href=\"https://www.cr.gov.hk/sc/home/index.htm\"><u>公司注册处 - 主页</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeo-1j9slu-645\"><img data-block-id=\"mlacddeo-00smni-646\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-m6z2ab3r.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t4-k1h2w0-293\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddep-c83ql1-647\">🇭🇰NAR1 - Annual Report </p><p data-block-id=\"mlacddep-f1p3nu-648\">(HK financial year Jul 1-Jun 30)</p><p data-block-id=\"mlacddep-8ztpjn-649\"><em>Note: Should there be corporate shareholders identified, we would also expect a copy of the merchant’s shareholding structure which includes UBO’s identified</em></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddep-73tgf0-650\"><img data-block-id=\"mlacddep-7pfj6c-651\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-w8evq3zi.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t4-cfl5oh-294\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddep-pz96fp-652\">Scanned ID Copy</p><p data-block-id=\"mlacddep-h704el-653\">/passport (both passport and ID accepted for Xtransfer merchants, for other Chinese merchants, accepting IF first and waiting for compliance feedback)</p><ul data-block-id=\"mlacddep-1o04lw-654\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacddep-co2eda-655\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t4-o47gdp-295\">Must be the correct format</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddep-inxvyn-656\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t4-gshb38-296\">Name must match authorized person’s name</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddep-vp82t5-657\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t4-svxe3s-297\">Must have an address, otherwise, MO must ask for proof of address</p></li></ul><p data-block-id=\"mlacddep-lie6cn-658\">Proof of address can be</p><ul data-block-id=\"mlacddep-v86l6i-659\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacddeq-74ebh3-660\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t4-xkfvh8-298\">Utility bill with address</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddeq-nov1wn-661\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t4-y0pgyc-299\">Tenancy agreement</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddeq-yeujjn-662\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t4-jkk1zj-300\">Photo of establishment with address </p></li></ul></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeq-b9wxjp-663\"><img data-block-id=\"mlacddeq-mqijg8-664\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-dv8r7xwy.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeq-v8a58c-665\"><img data-block-id=\"mlacddeq-emci71-666\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-eq1h325d.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeq-xcmj96-667\"><img data-block-id=\"mlacddeq-sot351-668\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-pggfrc8e.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t5-g4iqyx-301\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeq-ekmdpj-669\">🇨🇳Business License</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdder-padn59-670\"><img data-block-id=\"mlacdder-6wfbpk-671\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-z3qqmvfo.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"50\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t5-6q24lb-302\"></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdder-jgpmuv-672\">cnNational Enterprise Credit Information Publicity System</p><p data-block-id=\"mlacdder-bqdmzf-673\"><a href=\"https://www.gsxt.gov.cn/index.htm\"><u>国家企业信用信息公示系统</u></a></p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacdder-r0rrqw-674\">1, Search the entity in the database</p><p data-block-id=\"mlacdder-5j1ha9-675\"><img data-block-id=\"mlacdder-sepwdg-676\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-idxpn03c.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mlacddes-ut6tz5-677\">2, Compare the information with the CN Business license</p><p data-block-id=\"mlacddes-9zq9oz-678\"><img data-block-id=\"mlacddes-7zj07s-679\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-cj3lqjkp.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><p data-block-id=\"mlacddes-gtexk3-680\"><img data-block-id=\"mlacddes-beo3ws-681\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/aa-cn---draft-kyc-flow-image-wxa083jk.png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"false\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h2 data-block-id=\"mlacddes-74keg2-682\"><a id=\"_4c5qwx6te5uw\" display=\"false\"></a></h2><h2 data-block-id=\"mlacddes-w5pw6d-683\"><a id=\"_isaaym4iq0i6\" display=\"false\"></a>Requesting Resubmission</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"100%\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\"><colgroup style=\"display:none;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"><col style=\"width:250px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"4\" rowspan=\"1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"mlacddes-4hrx89-684\"><a id=\"_93yv97styywg\" display=\"false\"></a>Resubmission</h2></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddes-9z3knj-685\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddet-bzy1lh-686\">For additional communication except for emails, communicate to (a)Kai Li/(b) sales Kenzy to reach out Xtransfer. All resubmission documents will be received in the Admin Dashboard.</p><p data-block-id=\"mlacddet-533dh5-687\">Situations for resubmission request</p><ul data-block-id=\"mlacddet-pkgs0w-688\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacddet-qfboes-689\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t6-weutz1-303\">Additional documents needed</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddet-8tsprs-690\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t6-t52vob-304\">Incomplete/obscure documents</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddet-eqb7r9-691\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t6-sc1bsi-305\">Incomplete information on official sites, eg. legal name(not business name), address, price, etc</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddet-a9edzi-692\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t6-6uwt5r-306\">Unsure of the nature of business–ask for invoice to customer or explanation</p></li></ul></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddet-l82xf7-693\">MO, CPS, Sales</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"4\" rowspan=\"1\"><h2 data-block-id=\"mlacddet-4s9fli-694\"><a id=\"_4pfziuyttc9h\" display=\"false\"></a>After Resubmission</h2></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddet-jlbb86-695\">1</p></th><th colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeu-hsoyhk-696\">Check and tick/cross for resubmitted parts, go live if all parts are sufficient</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeu-dz8hif-697\">MO</p></th></tr><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeu-m2m8m6-698\">2</p></th><th colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddeu-swd7ru-699\">For insufficient cases:</p><ul data-block-id=\"mlacddeu-z41gtd-700\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacddeu-kbsl7n-701\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t7-1zj3y9-307\">Approach Hongjie for compliance related issues</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddev-av91j4-702\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t7-oryuq5-308\">Ask merchant/Rachel for next round resubmission if needed</p></li></ul></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddev-hx8c2w-703\">MO,Compliance</p></th></tr></tbody></table></div><h1 data-block-id=\"mlacddev-j7u8fe-704\"><a id=\"_e81ihs6wd6z8\" display=\"false\"></a></h1><h1 data-block-id=\"mlacddev-d2zkzn-705\"><a id=\"_a2rr4wmnm6vc\" display=\"false\"></a>FAQ</h1><h3 data-block-id=\"mlacddev-wbdrl4-706\"><a id=\"_xspg5kp77l0e\" display=\"false\"></a>Escalation point</h3><ol data-block-id=\"mlacddev-5v11kw-707\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacddev-iten8q-708\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t7-frkdse-309\">Open cases/True positive in ComplyAdvantage - raise to #compliance-request for compliance to check and give clearance</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddev-3hhhd7-709\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t7-8eqgb9-310\">Very high risk on Admin Dashboard - will raised to HJ for confirmation</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddev-xj2834-710\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t7-6lmn10-311\">Forgery documents - will raised to HJ for confirmation</p></li></ol><h1 data-block-id=\"mlacddev-l4nmcj-711\"><a id=\"_s3egzobe91p8\" display=\"false\"></a>High risk/prohibited industries</h1><p data-block-id=\"mlacddev-l7vo66-712\">*If the industry is prohibited in one market but not in the other, provide access case by case.</p><p data-block-id=\"mlacddev-ya3n3z-713\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1TkFVX3DtRnoTcI_AGN55TTRKU2upVz56rxIBoUSY09Q/edit?gid=136898357&amp;authuser=1#gid=136898357\"><u>https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1TkFVX3DtRnoTcI_AGN55TTRKU2upVz56rxIBoUSY09Q/edit?gid=136898357#gid=136898357</u></a></p><ol data-block-id=\"mlacddev-eivqpo-714\" start=\"1\" style=\"--start:0;\"><li data-block-id=\"mlacddev-gqowck-715\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t7-lxi2jr-312\">Crypto-High risk</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddev-lj4fbr-716\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t7-pgphs0-313\">Online gambling-Prohibited</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddev-cljki1-717\"><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t7-52swl0-314\">Firearms-Prohibited</p></li><li data-block-id=\"mlacddev-j66jdt-718\"><p data-block-id=\"mlacddex-t6glts-719\">Prostitution-Prohibited</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"mlant2t7-lpz8e4-315\"></p>","ContentType":2},{"Code":"id","Content":null,"ContentType":2},{"Code":"th","Content":null,"ContentType":2},{"Code":"es-mx","Content":null,"ContentType":2}]